msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "Sega - Saturn (Yabause)"
msgstr "Sega - Saturn (Yabause)"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "Yabause stands for Yet Another Buggy And Uncomplete Saturn Emulator. Yabause can boot Sega Saturn bios and games, some of which are playable."
msgstr "Yabause znamená Yet Another Buggy And Uncomplete Saturn Emulator. Yabause umí spustit BIOS a hry pro Sega Saturn, z nichž některé jsou hratelné."

